<p>One of the implementable solutions to this issue is the to create a common resource pool for office stationery. Items such as smaller note pads, refillable pens, etc. can be collected and stored in a common reserve to supply to all workers. When your need for a file is fulfilled, it can go back to the bin. Any item not used by you can be deposited for other’s usage. Sharing and making stationery a community resource can significantly reduce its wastage. </p>
