<p>The world is on the brink of degradation. Our actions can either timely intervene the damage or add to it. We need to make sustainable changes to our everyday routine, keeping the future in mind. These small changes will eventually become a cannonball of efforts that will hinder the damage being done to earth. </p>
<p>Educating the school children in environment is the need of the hour. When threated, we need our wits and sound knowledge to face the threat and win against it. Similarly, we need to provide tips, practices and information to the children with which they can face the future environment threats. </p>
